Applications of the Gas Detector Module:


1) This project can be used in home and hotel utility (kitchen) area for safety purpose.
2) Useful in domestic LPG water heater.
3) Very useful in LPG/CNG fitted car to avoid measure accident.
4) Prevent measure accident in gas agencies (gas station) where multi cylinder stored.
5) This system is very useful in hotels, home, car, LPG agencies. This system has advance safety standard and most important this helps prevent accident occurred because of fire.
























WORKING:


The working of any advanced system is mainly dependent on the microcontroller which controls the entire functioning of the device. In this case the Arduino Uno microcontroller acts like a conditional switch. It performs two set of action depending upon the condition present. It triggers the buzzer and the LED glows when the leakage of the gas is detected by the sensor. The other action is that LED does not glow when the leakage of the gas is not detected by the sensor. This device to make the stakeholders aware about the leakage of gas taking place at their house in their absence so that necessary actions can be implemented immediately to prevent an accident. MQ2 (LPG Gas) sensor is used to detect LPG leakage this sensor has quick response time it responding very short period of time. LED works when MQ2 crosses threshold level. And also a Buzzer is turned on to give Alert indication. We have provided a potentiometer which is used to vary the threshold level of comparator which decides the threshold level of leakage condition.
 
